resources.residConnectUpsellFlyoutText: Ka taea te tiro i ngā whakaahua me ngā ataata mai i ō pūrere, ratonga, whatunga pāpori hoki ki te wāhi kotahi.  Kia tīmata ai, tirohia kua tūhono koe ki te Ipurangi.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_EmptySourceView: Kua hunaia ō pūtake whakaahua katoa. Kia whakaaturia ētahi, hurihia ō tautuhinga.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_GenericDevice:
Ka whakaatu te taupānga Whakaahua i ō whakaahua me ō ataata mai i ō pūrere katoa i te wāhi kotahi.

Kia kite i ngā whakaahua me ngā ataata mai i tētahi atu RW, haere ki taua RW, ka haere ki SkyDrive.com/windows ki te tikiake me te tāuta i a Microsoft SkyDrive, takiuru me tō pūkete Microsoft, ka tirohia kia tīpako i te tautuhinga Tīkina ō kōnae mai i ngā wāhi katoa.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_Device: Mēnā kei a koe ētahi, āta whakarite kua huia e koe ki tō Puna Pikitia o {{%1}}.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_Service: Tāpiritia ētahi whakaahua ki tō pūkete kia tīmata.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_SkyDrive:
E tuku ana a SkyDrive i te rokiroki tuihono koreutu ki a koe mō ngā whakaahua, ngā ataata me ngā tuhinga e taea ai ērā e koe mai i ngā wāhi katoa.

Haere ki SkyDrive.com kia tīmata. Ko ngā whakaahua me ngā ataata e rokiroki koe ki reira ka whakaaturia ki konei.
resources.residEmptySourceMessage_PicturesLibrary:
Kia tīmata, tūhono mai he pūrere (kāmera, waea, puku kōhiko USB, ērā mea) ka kawemai, tārua rānei i ngā whakaahua me ngā ataata ki tō puna Pikitia.

Mēnā he whakaahua, he ataata kē rānei āu i tēnei RW, āta tirohia kei roto ēnā i tō puna Pikitia. Ka taea te whakahaere i tō Puna Pikitia mai i Pūtoro Kōnae.
